<li>J. Bhasker, A SystemC Primer, Second Edition, Star Galaxy Publishing, 2004. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0965039129" class="internal">ISBN 0965039129</a></li>
<li>D. C. Black, J. Donovan, SystemC: From the Ground Up, Springer 2005. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0387292403" class="internal">ISBN 0387292403</a></li>
<li>Frank Ghenassia (Editor), Transaction-Level Modeling with Systemc: Tlm Concepts and Applications for Embedded Systems, Springer 2006. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0387262326" class="internal">ISBN 0387262326</a></li>
</ol>
